Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.93,August,,0000,0000,0000,,August
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.93,September,,0000,0000,0000,,September
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:05.40,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,The role of the young
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:09.40,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,is to break new ground without fear of failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:11.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Break new ground, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.99,Feather,,0000,0000,0000,,Feather
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:17.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:21.16,Spoon,,0000,0000,0000,,Porcelain Spoon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:23.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you tryin' to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.50,Bowl2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice Bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:33.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Naru's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:34.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Naru hears, it won't be a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:39.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought we'd all throw a party for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:41.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an adult, so contribute a thousand yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:48.52,Cake,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCDE9F5&\fs16}Happy Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Party fees for a kid's birthday party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:46.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not party fees. It's the cake fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:48.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't buy a whole one with our pocket change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-nii will bring the food this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you get a present for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:54.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A present?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:57.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake! Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:57.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I have to write today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.95,Feather2,,0000,0000,0000,,Feather
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.95,Bowl3,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice Bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.95,Spoon2,,0000,0000,0000,,Porcelain Spoon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:01.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:19.66,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Barakamon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.01,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Onde
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:37.01,Barakamon Title Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Translation:\NBuddhist Prayer Dance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:38.84,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Your present is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.13,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,a teddy bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:42.39,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a punching bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:43.76,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A ribbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.14,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! It's perfect for \Nwrapping around my waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.02,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, a hand mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.40,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Laser Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:52.40,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:56.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,None of those suit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What would she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, cicada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:08.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a cicada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, got a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:14.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:15.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Need somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:16.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of need a favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only present I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I have a rhinoceros beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:23.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One! Just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you ten yen! \NThat's a lot for a kid, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer bein' a pest, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This present's for Naru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} givin' her rhinoceros beetles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one won't hurt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:37.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:42.86,Swarm,,0000,0000,0000,,Rustle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:41.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna give her a hundred \Nof 'em to make an insect bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like a punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't wanna give the \Nsame present as someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you giving her, Ichiro and Jiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make up names for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're givin' her sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've all thought on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You oughta think hard on it, too, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:01.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give her a stag beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can catch that many rhinoceros beetles,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then a stag beetle should be even easier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:07.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:11.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bug catchin' ain't as easy as ya think, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, {\i1}life{\i0} ain't that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You call it easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're tough to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:20.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're children, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With my adult's height,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see higher up, so it'll be easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, yer gettin' real irritatin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Found one right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, it's a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:36.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} spotted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:40.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle ain't over 'til the beetle's caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:41.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya can't catch even one rhinoceros beetle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's gonna be fed up with ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.53,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,So disappointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't exactly care, but I'm still irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, there's one over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I caught a rhinoceros beetle—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no I didn't! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a drone beetle, doofus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei can't catch nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A greater stag beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:18.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Formation Beta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:30.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:35.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:35.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you didn't leave yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean, "Thank you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave without catching one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I'm unbeatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:51.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can catch any bug, no matter how high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I've got my present!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you lend me the net real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You came bug catchin' when \Nyou won't even touch 'em?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! It might bite me, \Nor it could carry some weird disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't bite, and don't carry diseases!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to the beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Up close, it's even more gross than I imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:15.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so glossy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They ain't the same at all, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, give me the net, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:20.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might've bit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could a guy like this catch bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:33.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! It hurts! It hurts! It hurts, I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:34.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:38.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Hercules beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's one doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must've been \Nkeepin' it, but it got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be here otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, is it really that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}real{\i0} amazin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:48.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They showed 'em on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They cost 20,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.84,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,20,000 for a bug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, lend us the ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll join forces to catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru'll be thrilled to get such big game!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.28,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,20,000 for a kid's present...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go carefully, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:12.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No good... I can't reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:14.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?! No, I can't, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hold the ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An' we'll let Naru know how good you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:22.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give her the big game together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're beggin' ya, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:31.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep goin', Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:32.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just catch it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.19,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Hercules!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:42.27,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Hercules!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can ya fall twice in one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer clumsiness is a talent in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never trusting you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, got the Hercules?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:57.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I couldn't let it get away,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I held on tight to the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:06.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:09.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:10.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You smashed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:19.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you smashed the Hercules!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer dyin' next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}that{\i0} upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd say that because of some bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were gonna give it to Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry! Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:40.08,MX Handwritten,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurkules
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:54.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give ya one I caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:55.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:59.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. 'Cuz you worked hard for Naru's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:03.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never met an adult who'd play \Nseriously like you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:06.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have gobs of fun this summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:07.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:08.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:09.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab it from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:15.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:15.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:18.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I can hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:20.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm one step closer to your level!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never had any intention \Nof playing with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hate losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:28.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going at it seriously \Nfrom now on, so be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doin', dummy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.31,Birthday Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's {\c&H569351&}Turning {\c&H3429AD&}7
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My house...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.77,Cake,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru-chan\N{\c&HCDE9F5&}Happy Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is set up for the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer late, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you guys get into my house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years do ya think \Nwe've used this as our base?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have another of these,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:58.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:09:59.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A duplicate key!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:04.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the hardware store for a duplicate \Nbike key, and it was surprisingly cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made five of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's unlocked today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro! You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, if there are five of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who has the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:17.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe while playin' in the hills out back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, do you have a present ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought bubble wrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:31.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up some peacock feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:34.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really know what makes Naru tick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got bubble wrap, Miwa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But those feathers are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:40.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:41.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shoulda tried lookin' around—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:43.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:44.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time throwing a birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't have done it without you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:55.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this every year from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot off the cracker when she comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:13.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:14.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! It's my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, your present from Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:23.20,Birthday Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's {\c&H569351&}Turning {\c&H3429AD&}7
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, I'll give mine later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:30.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! From Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.84,Ticket2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ticket to do \Nanything you say
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.84,Ticket3,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut Here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.84,Ticket4,,0000,0000,0000,,One \Ntime
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! A grade schooler's \NMother's Day present?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:43.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's just one! So stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:44.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:47.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, it's okay to be mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.15,Ticket,,0000,0000,0000,,Ticket to do \Nanything you say\N\NOne time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:57.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm frightened by how thrilled you sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:10.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep watering these sunflowers, even though \NI have no idea who planted them or when.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I left them alone, they'd probably \Ngrow up fine on their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Climbing up there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grampa's goin' on a grave visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:23.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said to bring you along, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:24.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grave visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:25.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:32.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! This way, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:32.00,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.80,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already Obon season...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 'ere, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good of ya to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:42.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want an outsider \Nlike me at your family grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:45.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hafta go to the fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was thinkin' I'd have you keep \Nvigil over the gravesite flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:51.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Firecrackers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be bad omen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's normal 'round here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, a custom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care of the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:05.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru knows the ropes, so just do as she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, off to the fields!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:09.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He just dumped it on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:13.52,Gravesite,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoishi \NFamily \NGrave
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:13.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never made a proper grave visit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who's resting here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:19.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I hope you'll treat me well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, first ya gotta set the lan'ern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The "lan'ern"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, those!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, paper lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:26.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan'ern!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, \Nall the graves have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:32.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until this flame goes out, \Nwe mustn't leave the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:35.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are candles that burn for two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to stay here for that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got these in case we get bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I pay a visit, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yasuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to offer an incense stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:52.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was friends with Naru's gramma, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:02.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow or other, I managed \Nto live through this past year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.86,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda depressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There, much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:09.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, ya must have it rough in this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With an outsider like me here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:13.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's grandma probably can't rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:21.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See how the flame's dancin' up and down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:26.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That means her gramma's smilin' down on ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in yerself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll do my best, if it'll make \Nthe master of this grave happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:37.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:38.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:40.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're parachutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fallin' umbrellas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:55.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! Midair catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Miwa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Running wild without regard \Nfor anyone she's disturbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's hard to run in a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:06.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, those were the last fallin' umbrellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do somethin' else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:13.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Sensei, give us some reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just ignore us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's foul play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.67,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's telling us to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, we'll help, we'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop giving us the evil eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:28.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is different from Obon in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, we don't visit in the evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and we don't offer uncooked rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We also don't set off fireworks, \Nor wear yukata, or hang paper lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:43.46,Gravesite,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoishi \NFamily\N Grave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The gold gravestone lettering is strange, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:43.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer kiddin'! They ain't \Ngold everywhere in Japan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:47.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I rarely make grave visits,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:50.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't exactly talk like I'm \Nan expert on the customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:54.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we only come to visit \Ngraves during Obon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we really only come to set off fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and to see the {\i1}onde{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Onde?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D'ya mind if we proceed past your gravesite?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the onde. They dance at each family \Ngrave that's had a death since last Obon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're kinda scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:31.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean, translated into Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't exactly a foreign language.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.31,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Why'd he stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.90,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, isn't he looking my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.62,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He {\i0}is{\i1} looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.61,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I done something wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should see the look on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:58.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you frighten too easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the troop, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They were shorthanded, so I'm filling in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry to the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet are killin' me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just three more. Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Sensei. I still have dancing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to watch you dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:30.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's gradually starting to fit in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally actin' as Naru's guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried to avoid thinking about it much,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:40.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but didn't Sensei come here because he \Npunched someone eminent in calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What if his punishment were lifted?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished your summer homework yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to a degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme copy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Yer late, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks! Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:04.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's smoky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if we offer incense?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:09.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Village Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:13.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's gramma took good care \Nof us while she was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:16.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, from Kinoshita General Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I offer incense?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Miwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you leave our gravesite \Nalone to goof off here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:27.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Geh! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:30.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, tell him ya made me come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nuts! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:43.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom told me to take \Nincense to Naru's grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,May I offer some this year, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:45.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:52.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's grandma is really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each year, people take turns paying her a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:57.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Naru's grandpa is busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:01.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,until now, Naru's had to keep \Nvigil over the flame by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:06.20,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \NI've never seen Naru's parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! A pinwheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:09.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:13.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's been more fun than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:15.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, you brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:19.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was always boring waiting \Nfor grampa to get back,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:21.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but today I don't wanna leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then spend the night here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet I know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be 'cuz you're here, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna play, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.61,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized it since she's \Nalways with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:38.14,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But she gets lonely just like anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:43.00,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If I left her alone, she'd probably \Ngrow up fine on her own...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.23,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:48.36,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I'll look after her when I have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The flame went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already time to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The vigil went by fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're goin' now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandpa hasn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll extend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:08.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:11.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna keep playin' here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:15.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:16.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Sensei, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramma's smilin' too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:58.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pooch-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:22:00.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here to fish for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:03.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogs don't eat crayfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:08.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking like one of the locals, \Nfishing at the lake like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I'm still learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:13.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers seem to like you too, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:15.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not move here permanently?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:18.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:20.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:24.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when there's a place \Nthat accepts you as you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:26.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you feel like it's safe \Nto attempt the impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:29.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pooch-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.05,0:22:33.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat me to lobster once you're \Na big-shot calligrapher!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:37.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}do{\i0} eat crayfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:39.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the shopkeeper, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:43.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:45.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a dream, but it still made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:49.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pooch is female.
